ble (film)|Inescapable]]''\n| Paul\n| \n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Sky (film)|Sky]]''\n| Detective Ruther\n|\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1991\n| ''Payoff''\n| Young Mac\n| TV movie\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[Champs (TV series)|Champs]]''\n| Matt Mazzilli\n| Episodes: \"Breaking Up Is Hard to Do\" and \"For Art's Sake\"\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[Robin of Locksley (series)|Robin of Locksley]]''\n| Prince John, Jr.\n| TV movie\n|-\n| 1997\n| ''Ronnie & Julie''\n| Ronnie Monroe\n| TV movie\n|-\n| 1997\n| ''[[On the Edge of Innocence]]''\n| Sammy\n| TV movie\n|-\n| 1997\n| ''[[The Outer Limits (1995 TV series)|The Outer Limits]]''\n| Devon Taylor\n| Episode: \"[[Music of the Spheres (The Outer Limits)|Music of the Spheres]]\"\n|-\n| 1998\u20132003\n| ''[[Dawson's Creek]]''\n| Pacey Witter\n| 124 episodes\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| Jesse Grass\n| Voice; Episode: \"[[Lisa the Tree Hugger]]\"\n|-\n| 2001\n| ''[[Cubix]]''\n| Brian\n| Voice\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''Capitol Law''\n| Mark Clayton\n| Unsold CBS TV pilot\n|-\n| 2008\u20132013\n| ''[[Fringe (TV series)|Fringe]]''\n| [[Peter Bishop]]\n| 96 episodes\n|-\n| 2014\u20132018\n| ''[[The Affair (TV series)|The Affair]]''\n| Cole Lockhart\n| 43 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Gravity Falls]]''\n| Additional Voices\n| Episode: \"Weirdmageddon 3: Take Back the Falls\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt]]''\n| Purvis\n| Episode: \"Kimmy Goes to a Hotel!\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Years of Living Dangerously]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"Collapse of the Oceans\"\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[When They See Us]]''\n| Mickey Joseph\n| 3 episodes \n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Little Fires Everywhere (miniseries)|Little Fires Everywhere]]''\n| Bill Richardson\n| TV miniseries \n|-\n|}\n\n===Stage===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''Smart People''\n| Brian\n| New play by [[Lydia R. Diamond]] at