ite Award]]\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Actor \u2013 Motion Picture|Best Actor \u2013 Motion Picture]]\n| ''Aurora Borealis''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2007\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Awards]]\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture]]\n| ''Bobby''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2009\n| [[Teen Choice Award]]\n| Choice Actor Fantasy/Sci-Fi\n| ''[[Fringe (TV series)|Fringe]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2010\n| [[Genie Awards]]\n| [[Genie Award for Best Performance by an Actor in a Leading Role|Best Performance by an Actor in a Leading Role]]\n| ''[[One Week (2008 film)|One Week]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2010\n| [[Teen Choice Award]]\n| Choice Actor Fantasy/Sci-Fi\n| ''Fringe''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2011\n| [[Teen Choice Award]]\n| Choice Actor Fantasy/Sci-Fi\n| ''Fringe''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2012\n| [[Teen Choice Award]]\n| Choice Actor Fantasy/Sci-Fi\n| ''Fringe''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2013\n| [[Saturn Awards]]\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Actor on Television|Best Actor on Television]]\n| ''Fringe''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[42nd People's Choice Awards|People's Choice Awards]]\n| [[42nd People's Choice Awards#Television|Favorite Premium Cable TV Actor]]\n| ''[[The Affair (TV series)|The Affair]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2017\n| [[People's Choice Awards]]\n| Favorite Premium Series Actor\n| ''The Affair''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|2018\n|[[Drama League Award]]s\n|Distinguished Performance Award\n|''[[Children of a Lesser God (play)|Children of a Lesser God]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{IMDb name|0005045}}\n* [http://www.cbc.ca/thehour/videos.html?id=1006295904 Joshua Jackson] on [[The Hour (Canadian TV series)|The Hour]] with [[George Stroumboulopoulos]]\n\n<!--KEEP CANADIAN CATEGORIES - HE HAS DUAL CITIZENSHIP. -->\n{{ACCT Best Actor}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Jackson, Joshua}}\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[